The Comedy Central Roast of Somizi seems to be getting and better by the day. At this rate, the roast is becoming a not-to-be-missed event. GARETH CLIFF TO HOST ROAST OF SOMIZI! And now they have just added a Razzmatazz treatment with former Minister, Fikile Mbalula who will bring the spirit of “Asinavalo” to the upcoming roast. “I am looking forward to taking part in the Roast.  It promises to be an exciting razzmatazz experience.  This will be a chance to showcase the greatness of our ability to get together as people of Mzansi to laugh and connect,” said the former Minister of fun. DJ FRESH AND NOMZAMO MBATHA ADDED TO SOMIZI ROAST! The Comedy Central Roast of Somizi will take place on Thursday, 26 April 2018, at Gold Reef City’s Lyric Theatre, south of Johannesburg. Unfortunately, tickets are already sold out but you can still catch the action on Comedy Central (DStv channel 122) on Monday, 7 May 2018 at 21:00, followed by the extended, uncensored version available to Showmax subscribers from Tuesday, 8 May 2018. SKHUMBA AND KURT DARREN ADDED TO SOMIZI ROAST! 